    <HistoryItem name="blu by BCA Digital" desc="Feb 2020 – Apr 2024">
      <p class="pb-2 text-justify text-sm text-tapa-500">
        I spearheaded a cross-platform mobile application that enables our bank
        partner, BCA Digital, to provide comprehensive and complete digital
        banking services. Traditionally, banking requires on-site visits to
        banking establishments to open a bank account and do large transactions.
        The services eliminate this friction for our customers. Some financial
        services offered includes shared savings accounts, time deposit
        accounts, transfers, bill payments, and e-money top-ups.
      </p>
      <p class="pb-2 text-justify indent-4 text-sm text-tapa-500">
        Early in the development cycle, I was in charge of some of the earliest
        modules in the application, such as customer registration, multi-factor
        authentication, and online transfer. I also work on the application's
        reward system, video call integration for the KYC process, and
        application interface redesign.
      </p>
      <p class="pb-2 text-justify indent-4 text-sm text-tapa-500">
        The application utilizes the React Native framework, Redux (with Redux
        Saga middleware), a custom HTTP client that enables SSL Pinning, React
        I18n, React Navigation, React Hook Form, and extensive use of CSS-in-JS
        library using Styled System. The majority of the code is written in
        TypeScript for type safety. A smaller portion of native mobile code is
        written in Java on Android and Objective-C/Swift on iOS to interface
        directly with third-party native SDK.
      </p>
      <p class="pb-2 text-justify indent-4 text-sm text-tapa-500">
        The application is available for download through the Google Play Store
        and Apple App Store. The application has seen substantial user adoption
        and satisfaction, and the trend will likely continue.
      </p>
